---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---
<Container>
<div class="relative flex flex-col items-center md:flex-row" id="projects">
    <div class="row items-center py-5 md:pr-40 md:w-5/12 md:py-10">
        <div class="text-center md:text-left space-y-3 bg-lime">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-medium leading-none sm:text-6xl">Case Studies</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center py-5 md:w-7/12 md:py-10">
        <p class="text-xl font-normal leading-7 text-center md:text-left">Real-world AI and data solutions delivered across energy, mining, government, finance, and media — from architecture to production.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

    <!-- Imdex -->
    <div class="p-10 bg-zinc-900 rounded-[45px] text-white flex flex-col gap-6 justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-lime text-black text-sm rounded-full font-medium">AI / Data Mesh</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-700 text-white text-sm rounded-full">Mining Tech</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">Global AI Agentic Data Mesh</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-normal leading-7 text-zinc-300">Established a global data platform, team structure, and operating model for Imdex — overseeing architecture delivery across Kubernetes, Snowflake, Kafka, Airflow, and DBT.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="justify-start items-center gap-[15px] inline-flex">
                <div class="text-lime text-xl font-normal leading-7">Discuss a similar project</div>
                <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow">
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Synergy -->
    <div class="p-10 bg-zinc-900 rounded-[45px] text-white flex flex-col gap-6 justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-lime text-black text-sm rounded-full font-medium">IoT / AI</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-700 text-white text-sm rounded-full">Energy</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">Rooftop Solar DER Virtual Power Plant</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-normal leading-7 text-zinc-300">Designed and delivered residential solar inverter telemetry ingestion and a bitemporal XTDB datastore for Synergy using Azure Databricks, DAPR microservices, and a CSIP-AUS compliant OT cloud architecture for DER grid forecasting.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="justify-start items-center gap-[15px] inline-flex">
                <div class="text-lime text-xl font-normal leading-7">Discuss a similar project</div>
                <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow">
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Dept of Education WA -->
    <div class="p-10 bg-zinc-900 rounded-[45px] text-white flex flex-col gap-6 justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-lime text-black text-sm rounded-full font-medium">~75% cost reduction</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-700 text-white text-sm rounded-full">Government</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">FinOps Cloud Cost Optimisation</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-normal leading-7 text-zinc-300">Delivered a FinOps program for the WA Department of Education across Azure, AWS, and Oracle — achieving approximately 75% reduction in billed cloud costs alongside a governance and reporting framework.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="justify-start items-center gap-[15px] inline-flex">
                <div class="text-lime text-xl font-normal leading-7">Discuss a similar project</div>
                <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow">
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- WA Dept Water -->
    <div class="p-10 bg-zinc-900 rounded-[45px] text-white flex flex-col gap-6 justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-lime text-black text-sm rounded-full font-medium">Architecture Leadership</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-700 text-white text-sm rounded-full">Government</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">Environment Online Program</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-normal leading-7 text-zinc-300">Led architecture across CRM, integration, and data workstreams for the WA Department of Water & Environmental Regulation — delivering governance guardrails and digital government services on Dynamics 365 and Power Platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="justify-start items-center gap-[15px] inline-flex">
                <div class="text-lime text-xl font-normal leading-7">Discuss a similar project</div>
                <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow">
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- South32 -->
    <div class="p-10 bg-zinc-900 rounded-[45px] text-white flex flex-col gap-6 justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-lime text-black text-sm rounded-full font-medium">Cloud + OT/IoT</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-700 text-white text-sm rounded-full">Mining</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">Cloud & OT/IoT Portfolio Re-Architecture</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-normal leading-7 text-zinc-300">Re-architected South32's capital project portfolio to cloud with IoT Edge reporting for SCADA and OT sensor systems — connecting operational technology to cloud analytics at scale across mining operations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="justify-start items-center gap-[15px] inline-flex">
                <div class="text-lime text-xl font-normal leading-7">Discuss a similar project</div>
                <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow">
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Fair Go Finance -->
    <div class="p-10 bg-zinc-900 rounded-[45px] text-white flex flex-col gap-6 justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-lime text-black text-sm rounded-full font-medium">FinTech / AI</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-700 text-white text-sm rounded-full">Finance</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">FinTech AI Credit Decisioning Platform</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-normal leading-7 text-zinc-300">Built an Azure PaaS microservices platform including Fasti online credit decisioning, a customer portal, the Viso data warehouse, and Annie risk analytics engine — delivering full-stack FinTech from the ground up.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="justify-start items-center gap-[15px] inline-flex">
                <div class="text-lime text-xl font-normal leading-7">Discuss a similar project</div>
                <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow">
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bankwest -->
    <div class="p-10 bg-zinc-900 rounded-[45px] text-white flex flex-col gap-6 justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-lime text-black text-sm rounded-full font-medium">Digital Banking</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-700 text-white text-sm rounded-full">Financial Services</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">Digital Banking Delivery & Compliance Remediation</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-normal leading-7 text-zinc-300">Led engineering and product delivery at Bankwest across payments, mobile tools, online lending, and CRM — including Royal Commission compliance remediation under tight regulatory timelines.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="justify-start items-center gap-[15px] inline-flex">
                <div class="text-lime text-xl font-normal leading-7">Discuss a similar project</div>
                <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow">
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Club Assist -->
    <div class="p-10 bg-zinc-900 rounded-[45px] text-white flex flex-col gap-6 justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-lime text-black text-sm rounded-full font-medium">20+ integrations</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-700 text-white text-sm rounded-full">Retail / Membership</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">APAC IT Modernisation & Supply Chain Integration</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-normal leading-7 text-zinc-300">Principal Integration Architect for Club Assist's APAC modernisation — delivering 20+ external supply-chain integrations and legacy system migration across Dynamics 365 CE/FO, BizTalk, and Azure Integration Services over three years.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="justify-start items-center gap-[15px] inline-flex">
                <div class="text-lime text-xl font-normal leading-7">Discuss a similar project</div>
                <img src="/services/agc.svg" alt="arrow">
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

</Container>
